name: Four Year Strong
description: '''Four Year Strong''' is an American [[pop-punk]] band from [[Worcester, Massachusetts]], formed in 2001. The group consists of vocalists and guitarists Dan O'Connor and Alan Day, bassist Joe Weiss, and drummer Jake Massucco. They have released eight studio albums; their most recent album, ''Analysis Paralysis'', was released on August 9, 2024, through [[Pure Noise Records]].
